  "lyrics": "Hey there, lookin' at me, just lightin' me, just a sight of you inside of me, and then\nI'm inserted into you.\nOoh, now we're walkin' through the waters and the oceans of our own desires, and how\nhigh we take each other, so hey girl, why you trippin' on me, trippin' on me, bleedin'\nme dry from me, I said, hey girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me, why aren't you free for\nyou, to make the same mistakes, to make me better than you think, teach me instead of\nerase me, fact don't change me, girl, I take the mind from me, just want you to see positively,\nall the words and ways that you take me down, girl, you're trippin' on the thought of being\nbetter than that, stay superficial and we can't be that, girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me,\nwhy you trippin' on me, yeah, hey girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me, why you wastin' me,\nwhy you takin' me and my light away from the world, why you takin' this light away from\nthe world, why you takin' me away from the world, why you takin' this light away from the world,\nooh, yeah, why you trippin' on me, why you takin' this light away from the world,\nall through the darkness we go down the drain, until you don't make the frown and you make\nthe mistake of throwing me away, said, hey, girl, yeah, I said, hey, girl, hey, girl, why you trippin'\non me, ooo, you trippin' on me, you trippin' on me, you trippin' on me, yeah, hey, girl, girl, girl, girl,\nrun away from me, cause I got the power to feed your selfish seed, your narcissistic ways, don't\nstand a chance with me?",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 21.459999084472656,
      "text": "Hey there, lookin' at me, just lightin' me, just a sight of you inside of me, and then",
      "start": 13.199999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 24.079999923706055,
      "text": "I'm inserted into you.",
      "start": 21.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 33.279998779296875,
      "text": "Ooh, now we're walkin' through the waters and the oceans of our own desires, and how",
      "start": 24.079999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 45.31999969482422,
      "text": "high we take each other, so hey girl, why you trippin' on me, trippin' on me, bleedin'",
      "start": 33.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 58.779998779296875,
      "text": "me dry from me, I said, hey girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me, why aren't you free for",
      "start": 45.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 65.23999786376953,
      "text": "you, to make the same mistakes, to make me better than you think, teach me instead of",
      "start": 59.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 72.22000122070312,
      "text": "erase me, fact don't change me, girl, I take the mind from me, just want you to see positively,",
      "start": 65.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 80.41999816894531,
      "text": "all the words and ways that you take me down, girl, you're trippin' on the thought of being",
      "start": 72.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 90.69999694824219,
      "text": "better than that, stay superficial and we can't be that, girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me,",
      "start": 80.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 104.16999816894531,
      "text": "why you trippin' on me, yeah, hey girl, ooh, why you trippin' on me, why you wastin' me,",
      "start": 92.02999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 112.01000213623047,
      "text": "why you takin' me and my light away from the world, why you takin' this light away from",
      "start": 104.3499984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 120.61000061035156,
      "text": "the world, why you takin' me away from the world, why you takin' this light away from the world,",
      "start": 112.01000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 131.92999267578125,
      "text": "ooh, yeah, why you trippin' on me, why you takin' this light away from the world,",
      "start": 124.05000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 139.1300048828125,
      "text": "all through the darkness we go down the drain, until you don't make the frown and you make",
      "start": 132.61000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 158.14999389648438,
      "text": "the mistake of throwing me away, said, hey, girl, yeah, I said, hey, girl, hey, girl, why you trippin'",
      "start": 139.1300048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 170.2100067138672,
      "text": "on me, ooo, you trippin' on me, you trippin' on me, you trippin' on me, yeah, hey, girl, girl, girl, girl,",
      "start": 158.14999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 178.27000427246094,
      "text": "run away from me, cause I got the power to feed your selfish seed, your narcissistic ways, don't",
      "start": 170.2100067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 181.41000366210938,
      "text": "stand a chance with me?",
      "start": 178.27000427246094
    }
  ],
